co.cask.cdap.etl.api

Interface Joiner<JOIN_KEY,INPUT_RECORD,OUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    JOIN_KEY - type of the join key
    INPUT_RECORD - type of input records to be joined
    OUT - type of output object
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BatchJoiner

    @Beta
public interface Joiner<JOIN_KEY,INPUT_RECORD,OUT>
    Provides join keys on which join needs to be performed and merges the join results.

        Merges records present in joinResult and returns merged output.
        Parameters:
